THIS CLASS IS CURRENTLY NOT USED AND THEREFORE ITS INTERFACE CANNOT BE GUARENTEED

The DBUserGroup class serves as the interface layer to the UserGroup table in the database for the relationship between Users and Groups in the datamodel.
